    "body": "Looking at the code, it appears to have been introduced in this PR:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/19669/files\r\n\r\nI expect this line:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/08e5cd94a9be9743617f0edbbd4c21ca93cc0911/internal/ethapi/api.go#L994\r\n\r\nShould be:\r\n\r\n```fields[\"size\"] = hexutil.Uint64(block.Size())```",
